---
import Layout from '~/layouts/Layout.astro'
import Hero from '~/features/hero_section/Hero.astro'
---

<Layout
	title="Boost Conversions with Straight 100 Scores on Google Lighthouse: Expert Web Solutions & Insightful Analytics"
	description="Elevate your online business with RPTrainor's custom-engineered web solutions. Transition from 'no code' limitations to high-performance landing pages designed to maximize conversions and sales with top Google Lighthouse scores. Experience the difference that expertly optimized web pages can make in achieving your business goals."
>
	<main class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4">
		<Hero />
		<div class="flex w-full flex-nowrap items-center justify-center gap-4">
			<svg
				xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
				fill="none"
				viewBox="0 0 24 24"
				stroke-width="2"
				stroke="currentColor"
				class="h-8 w-8 animate-bounce"
			>
				<path
					stroke-linecap="round"
					stroke-linejoin="round"
					d="M19.5 13.5 12 21m0 0-7.5-7.5M12 21V3"></path>
			</svg>
			<svg
				xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
				fill="none"
				viewBox="0 0 24 24"
				stroke-width="2"
				stroke="currentColor"
				class="h-12 w-12 animate-spin"
			>
				<path
					stroke-linecap="round"
					stroke-linejoin="round"
					d="M12 6v12m-3-2.818.879.659c1.171.879 3.07.879 4.242 0 1.172-.879 1.172-2.303 0-3.182C13.536 12.219 12.768 12 12 12c-.725 0-1.45-.22-2.003-.659-1.106-.879-1.106-2.303 0-3.182s2.9-.879 4.006 0l.415.33M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z"
				></path>
			</svg>
			<svg
				xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
				fill="none"
				viewBox="0 0 24 24"
				stroke-width="2"
				stroke="currentColor"
				class="h-8 w-8 animate-bounce"
			>
				<path
					stroke-linecap="round"
					stroke-linejoin="round"
					d="M19.5 13.5 12 21m0 0-7.5-7.5M12 21V3"></path>
			</svg>
		</div>
		<section class="grid grid-cols-1 place-content-center place-items-center sm:grid-cols-2">
			<div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4">
				<h2>The Cost of Slow Performance</h2>
				<p>
					Slow websites are a major turn-off for users. A 1-second delay in page load time can
					result in a 7% reduction in conversions. This means that if an e-commerce site is making
					$100,000 per day, a 1-second page delay could potentially cost $2.5 million in lost sales
					every year.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4"></div>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>
